        <item>
            <title>【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI Summit E13 AI Evo AI 登场，搭载 Intel Core Ultra 7 处理器 155H</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-summit-e13-ai-evo-ai/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=msi-summit-e13-ai-evo-ai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-summit-e13-ai-evo-ai/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI Summit E13 AI Evo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Summit E13 AI Evo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1240823</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">一年一度的 Computex 台北国际电脑展引来不少大厂推出新机，MSI 推出最新款 Summit E13 AI Evo AI 手提电脑，搭载最新 Intel Core Ultra 7 处理器 155H，Intel Arc  显示卡。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240824 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-10-694x478.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="478" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-10-694x478.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1240825 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-11-694x472.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-11-694x472.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240605at-11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲Summit E13 AI Evo 搭载最新 Intel Core Ultra 7 处理器 155H，Intel Arc 显示卡</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Summit E13 AI Evo，重量为 1.39kg，厚度约 15.9 &#8211; 16.2mm。Summit E13 AI Evo 配备 1TB*1 NVMe SSD PCIe Gen4 储存空间。配上了 13.3 吋 FHD 1920&#215;1200 触控萤幕，MSI Precision Pen Touch Technology 、100%sRGB 色域， 并支援 MSI Pen 2 。Summit E13 AI Evo 拥有多种连接埠，包括  HDMI™ 2.1（4K @ 60Hz）、两个支援 Thunderbolt  4 USB Type-C 连接埠、一个 Type-A USB3.2 Gen1 连接埠。Summit E13 AI Evo 支援 Wi-Fi 7 技术，确保高速网络连接和低延迟。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Summit E13 AI Evo 与其他 AI 手提电脑一样配备了 Copilot Key，可启动 Windows Copilot 功能。MSI 的 AI 智能引擎可以就不同情境并自动调整硬件设定，加上有升级的 AI 降噪技术及三咪高峰阵列设计，可在噪杂的环境中听到清晰音效。Summit 系列亦提供 3D Noise Reduction + 及 AI Noise Cancellation Pro 技术，可享更优质会议体验。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/20/msi-claw-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】MSI Claw　外形　手感　效能　打机体验　散热　屏幕 5 大优点 + 缺点开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/05/msi-lunar-lake-prestige-ai-pc/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【Computex 2024】MSI 发布一系列 AI PC　同场加映 18 吋 Mercedes-AMG 联乘笔电</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/04/msiclaw8aiplus-withlunarlake/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI Claw 8 AI Plus      Intel Lunar Lake 处理器 + 80Wh 大容量电池</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/msi-summit-e13-ai-evo-ai/notebook/">【COMPUTEX 2024】MSI Summit E13 AI Evo AI 登场，搭载 Intel Core Ultra 7 处理器 155H</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
